Congrats #California you did it again!! We closed on our new home Feb 1 🥂We are officially TN residents ! Crime matters & Money goes where it's appreciated. 🤑Two Lessons you STILL haven't figured out. Will always love you,but we will just have to agree on keeping it a summer love for now. 🌊☀️

I always say; move with your feet and wallet, not with your lips. Enough finally became enough for us and it was time to go a state that better aligns with our values. Love CA and always will, but the truth is it's just not the same. People are not safe. Crime is skyrocketing,and nobody cares. Voters have spoken. They had one last chance in LA last year to implement change and blew it.Taxes will continue to rise to in order to support a growing agenda that rewards mediocrity and penalizes hard work and ethics. Not with our money any more. See you in the summer 😎

#Upgradeyourlife #values #wealthmindset #realtalk #Nashville #Tn #wakeupca #takeaction #tennessee #politics #voteforchange
